text: Wyrc sealfe wið ælfcynne and nihtgengan and þam mannum þe deofol mid hæmð.
Genim eowohumelan, wermod, bisceopwyrt, elehtre, æscþrote, beolone, harewyrt, haransprecel, hæþbergean wisan, cropleac, garleac, hegerifan corn, gyþrife, finul.
Do þas wyrta on an fæt, sete under weofod, sing ofer IX mæssan, awyl on buteran and on sceapes smerwe, do haliges sealtes fela on, aseoh þurh clað, weorp þa wyrta on yrnende wæter.
Gif men hwilc yfel costung weorþe, oþþe ælf oþþe nihtgengan, smire his andwlitan mid þisse sealfe, and on his eagan do and þær him se lichoma sar sie.
And recelsa hine and sena gelome.
